<p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Çetin Teknoloji Ltd.Sti. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">("Lazimbana"), we are working to protect the privacy of our members who use our site to ensure that our users benefit safely and completely from our services. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In this respect, ibu Lazimbana Privacy Policy ("Policy") has been prepared in order to inform our members of our personal data in a manner fully compliant with the Law No. 6698 on Personal Data Protection ("Law") and to inform our users accordingly. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The lazimbana.com cookie policy is an integral part of the Isbu Policy.</font></font><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
